org.sql: SELECT members.* FROM members INNER JOIN projects ON projects.id = members.project_id WHERE members.user_id = "$1" AND projects.status <> "$2" AND projects.status <> 9

rewrites.sql: SELECT members.* FROM members INNER JOIN projects ON projects.id = members.project_id WHERE members.user_id = "$1" AND projects.status <> "$2" AND projects.status <> 9 LIMIT 1
